	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Salman Rushdie&amp;nbsp;British writer born in India.&lt;/strong&gt; Realistic characters, unforgettable humor, enthusiasm, and melodramatic prose to examine the style of historical and philosophical issues.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Salman Rushdie is the author of thirteen novels:&lt;/strong&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
